sk.stu.fiit.data

Class Lists

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.stu.fiit.data.Lists
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Lists
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Class Lists serves as class storing all information given from GUI. Stores Arrays of registered Users, Leagues and Teams. Also checks if given inputs are valid when creating classes, returns lists and allows needed kinds of filtering.
    See Also:
    User, League, Team, Serialized Form
